title: Dishwasher Upper Rack Slide
description: Dishwasher Upper Rack Slide PartSelect Number PS261576 Manufacturer Part Number WD30X98 This slide is mounted to each side of the upper cabinet wall. The dishrack wheels roll inside this track, which guides the upper rack.

installationInstructions.author: Dave from Littleton, CO
installationInstructions.title: Parts were old and worn out
installationInstructions.content: The repair was easy. A couple turns of a screwdriver was all that was necessary to remove the rollers and slide assembly. The I simple installed the new rollers. Slid the slide into place between the rollers and then added the back caps to the slide.  Replaced the rack rollers on the top basket and then slid it into position between the new slides. Once in place, I attached the end caps to the front of the slide. Simple and quick.
